<h1>Shoebox Appeal Products</h1>
  <p>As with our regular offline Shoeobox Appeal Project, also online, you are able to customize your shoebox present as much as you'd like.</p>
  <p>Just choose from the items below, divided into "men" "women" and "kids" and create your own shoebox with an individualized message for your receipient.</p>

<table class='catalog'>
  <% @products.each do |product| %>
   <tr>
      <td>
        <div class='image'>
          <%= link_to (image_tag product.image_url, :style =>'height:100px'), product %>
        </div>
      </td>
  <td>
          <div class='title'>
            <%= link_to product.product, product%>
          </div>
          <div class='description'>
            <%= product.description %>
          </div>
          <div class='price'>
            <%= number_to_currency(product.price, :unit => 'â‚¬') %>
          </div>
          
          
          <div class='links'>
            <% if current_user.admin? %>
              <td><%= link_to 'Edit', edit_product_path(product) %></td>
              <td><%= link_to 'Destroy', product, method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' } %></td>
          <% else %>
            <a href='/cart'<% products.id %>Add to Cart</a><br><br>
          <% end %>
          </div>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <% end %>
</table>          
          
  <br>
   <% if current_user.admin? %>
   <%= link_to 'New Product', new_product_path %>
   <% end %>    
